The '''Executive Level''' was a level of the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|first Death Star]].

It contained exercise suites with [[Heavy Gravity Room]]s. [[Conan Antonio Motti/Legends|Conan Antonio Motti]] worked out in one Heavy Gravity Room where he would set it at 3Gs. [[Grand Moff/Legends|Grand Moff]] [[Wilhuff Tarkin/Legends|Wilhuff Tarkin's]] quarters were located on the Executive Level where he boasted hot water showers versus conventional [[Sonic shower/Legends|sonic showers]].

